# -*- mode: python ; coding: utf-8 -*-
"""PyInstaller spec file for PetaKit (Windows).

CuPy imports are walker-traced (installer/cupy_walker.py) to bundle only
the modules petakit actually uses — saves ~32 MB by excluding cudnn,
cusolver, cusparse, cutensor, nccl, curand, jitify.

IMPORTANT: Run from the installer/ directory:
  cd installer && python -m PyInstaller petakit_windows.spec --noconfirm
"""

